    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dust your work surface with a generous sprinkling of<strong> flour</strong></p><p>Unwrap your <strong>puff pastry</strong> and roll it out to approx. 1 cm thickness with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> and cut into 1 rectangle per person</p><p>Press the <strong>halved asparagus</strong> into the pastry diagonally and crimp the borders with a fork</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-copy-3-1647965943215-x200.jpg",
