    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>pastry rectangle[s]</strong> to a <strong>non-stick baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!)</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 15 min or until the pastry is puffed up, golden and cooked through – this is your <strong>asparagus pie lid</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
